text: River Heights may refer to: * River Heights, Utah, a city in Cache County, Utah * River Heights (electoral district), a provincial electoral division in the Canadian province of Manitoba * River Heights, Winnipeg, a neighborhood of Winnipeg, Manitoba in roughly the same area as the riding above * River Heights, Saskatoon, an area of Saskatoon, Saskatchewan * River Heights, Nancy Drew's fictional home town in Midwestern United States. *River Heights (Nancy Drew), a spinoff series from the original Nancy Drew series
